title: Wall Lamps
body: Place any of Mobelaris wall lamps in your house for a classic and balanced look. Our hardworking team aimed toward providing a great selection of Mid-Century, Scandinavian, 20th Century Bauhaus and progressive contemporary style designs at competitive prices. We have remove the intervention of middlemen and their hefty pricing to make sure that you only pay the right amount without compromising the quality. Feel free to browse in our catalogs as we constantly update our product line to suit your taste and budget.
